**Why orange-red:** Studies show warm colors (red, orange, yellow) increase appetite and urgency. Every major food brand uses them — DoorDash (red), UberEats (black+green), Grubhub (orange).

**Dark mode version:**
bg: #1a1410 (warm dark brown, not blue-black), surface: rgba(255,220,180,0.04), primary stays warm.

